## ğŸ› Troubleshooting

**Can't login?**
- Check your email and password
- Make sure you registered first

**Nothing showing up?**
- Clear browser cache (Ctrl + Shift + Delete)
- Try a different browser

**Other issues?**
- Check GitHub issues page
- Contact via GitHub

